*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.tgz binary

# ML
